data.description: Well maintained and spacious 3-4 bedroom, 2 full bath home in the Licking Valley area. This home is in great shape and sits on .55 acres. Large kitchen is loaded with beautiful cabinets and an island/bar that looks out onto the large dining room. Plenty of living space with the large living room upstairs and the rec room in the lower level. Lower back porch area has been enclosed and is ready for you to complete for even more living space. Come take a look and make this home your. Property is being sold 'as-is'.
